msgctxt "112_Akiyama"
msgid "I've got an idea. Let's use my hundred bil."
msgstr "I've got an idea. Let's use my hundred bil."

msgctxt "124_Date"
msgid "...How, exactly?"
msgstr "...How, exactly?"

msgctxt "136_Akiyama"
msgid "It's simple. We haul it up to the roof of the Millennium\\r\n"
"Tower, then kick back and wait."
msgstr "It's simple. We haul it up to the roof of the Millennium\\r\n"
"Tower, then kick back and wait."

msgctxt "148_Tanimura"
msgid "What, that's it?"
msgstr "What, that's it?"

msgctxt "160_Akiyama"
msgid "That's it."
msgstr "Ya está."

msgctxt "172_Date"
msgid "Back it up a sec. What's that accomplish?"
msgstr "Back it up a sec. What's that accomplish?"

msgctxt "184_Akiyama"
msgid "It'll bring all the flies buzzing straight into our web."
msgstr "It'll bring all the flies buzzing straight into our web."

msgctxt "196_Kiryu"
msgid "Flies?"
msgstr "Flies?"

msgctxt "208_Akiyama"
msgid "Not literally. I'm talking about our enemies."
msgstr "Not literally. I'm talking about our enemies."

msgctxt "220_Tanimura"
msgid "That's kind of a broad term. Who exactly are you thinking is\\r\n"
"gonna show?"
msgstr "That's kind of a broad term. Who exactly are you thinking is\\r\n"
"gonna show?"

msgctxt "232_Akiyama"
msgid "Not sure. We'll just have to wait and find out."
msgstr "Not sure. We'll just have to wait and find out."

msgctxt "244_Date"
msgid "...Huh? You're not making any sense, man."
msgstr "...Huh? You're not making any sense, man."

msgctxt "256_Akiyama"
msgid "Just hold on a second. Think about everyone we know who's\\r\n"
"wrapped up in all this. Munakata, Arai-san, Kido-chan, the\\r\n"
"Tojo."
msgstr "Just hold on a second. Think about everyone we know who's\\r\n"
"wrapped up in all this. Munakata, Arai-san, Kido-chan, the\\r\n"
"Tojo."

msgctxt "268_Akiyama"
msgid "All those parties are playing different roles in this little\\r\n"
"performance... but we still don't know who's the real ringleader."
msgstr "All those parties are playing different roles in this little\\r\n"
"performance... but we still don't know who's the real ringleader."

msgctxt "280_Akiyama"
msgid "Until we get them all in one place, laying it all on the line... we're just gonna be shooting in the dark."
msgstr "Until we get them all in one place, laying it all on the line... we're just gonna be shooting in the dark."

msgctxt "292_Kiryu"
msgid "So we'll lure them out to find out who's really in charge."
msgstr "So we'll lure them out to find out who's really in charge."

msgctxt "304_Akiyama"
msgid "Exactly. We tell each party that we're keeping the cash on the roof of the Millennium Tower... and they can come up and make a deal with us if they want a slice of the pie."
msgstr "Exactly. We tell each party that we're keeping the cash on the roof of the Millennium Tower... and they can come up and make a deal with us if they want a slice of the pie."

msgctxt "316_Akiyama"
msgid "We play our cards right, they all slam headfirst into each\\r\n"
"other."
msgstr "We play our cards right, they all slam headfirst into each\\r\n"
"other."

msgctxt "328_Tanimura"
msgid "And then they'll duke it out over the money."
msgstr "And then they'll duke it out over the money."

msgctxt "340_Akiyama"
msgid "Yup. Though I don't really care if they fight or not."
msgstr "Yup. Though I don't really care if they fight or not."

msgctxt "352_Akiyama"
msgid "All that matters is that we figure out who the big bad is."
msgstr "All that matters is that we figure out who the big bad is."

msgctxt "364_Akiyama"
msgid "From then on it'll just be a good old-fashioned beatdown."
msgstr "From then on it'll just be a good old-fashioned beatdown."

msgctxt "376_Kiryu"
msgid "That's my kind of plan."
msgstr "That's my kind of plan."

msgctxt "388_Tanimura"
msgid "That's the what and where settled, then. What about the\\r\n"
"when?"
msgstr "That's the what and where settled, then. What about the\\r\n"
"when?"

msgctxt "400_Akiyama"
msgid "Well, it's gonna take a while to haul all those stacks up\\r\n"
"there. And I'm sure all of you have stuff you wanna handle\\r\n"
"before we execute the plan."
msgstr "Well, it's gonna take a while to haul all those stacks up\\r\n"
"there. And I'm sure all of you have stuff you wanna handle\\r\n"
"before we execute the plan."

msgctxt "412_Akiyama"
msgid "How about we go our separate ways for a while, grab some\\r\n"
"food, hit up a few convenience stores, then meet back here\\r\n"
"when we're ready?"
msgstr "How about we go our separate ways for a while, grab some\\r\n"
"food, hit up a few convenience stores, then meet back here\\r\n"
"when we're ready?"

msgctxt "424_Tanimura"
msgid "Works for me."
msgstr "Works for me."

msgctxt "436_Kiryu"
msgid "Sounds like a plan."
msgstr "Sounds like a plan."

msgctxt "460_Tanimura"
msgid "You good with that, Saejima-san?"
msgstr "You good with that, Saejima-san?"

msgctxt "472_Saejima"
msgid "...Yeah. I'm in."
msgstr "...Yeah. I'm in."

msgctxt "532_Haruka"
msgid "Uncle Kaz."
msgstr "Tío Kaz."

msgctxt "544_Kiryu"
msgid "Haruka. What's wrong? Did something happen?"
msgstr "Haruka. ¿Pasa algo malo? ¿Sucedió algo?"

msgctxt "556_Haruka"
msgid "Uncle Kaz. Hamazaki-san, he..."
msgstr "Uncle Kaz. Hamazaki-san, he..."

msgctxt "568_Kiryu"
msgid "Hamazaki? What happened to him?"
msgstr "Hamazaki? What happened to him?"

msgctxt "580_Haruka"
msgid "He's... He's gone. He just passed away in the hospital."
msgstr "He's... He's gone. He just passed away in the hospital."

msgctxt "592_Kiryu"
msgid "What?"
msgstr "¿Qué?"

msgctxt "604_Haruka"
msgid "According to the doctor, the cause of death was a gunshot\\r\n"
"wound to the back."
msgstr "According to the doctor, the cause of death was a gunshot\\r\n"
"wound to the back."

msgctxt "616_Kiryu"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "628_Haruka"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "640_Kiryu"
msgid "All right, I understand. Thanks for being there in his final\\r\n"
"moments, Haruka."
msgstr "All right, I understand. Thanks for being there in his final\\r\n"
"moments, Haruka."

msgctxt "652_Haruka"
msgid "You don't have to thank me for that. And hey... Uncle Kaz?"
msgstr "You don't have to thank me for that. And hey... Uncle Kaz?"

msgctxt "664_Kiryu"
msgid "Hm? What is it?"
msgstr "¿Qué? ¿Qué es esto?"

msgctxt "676_Haruka"
msgid "Hamazaki-san died protecting you, didn't he?"
msgstr "Hamazaki-san died protecting you, didn't he?"

msgctxt "688_Kiryu"
msgid "...Yeah, it seems like it. He sacrificed his life for us."
msgstr "...Yeah, it seems like it. He sacrificed his life for us."

msgctxt "700_Haruka"
msgid "Then... I wish I could tell him how sorry I am. I was so\\r\n"
"wrong about him."
msgstr "Then... I wish I could tell him how sorry I am. I was so\\r\n"
"wrong about him."

msgctxt "712_Kiryu"
msgid "It's okay, Haruka."
msgstr "It's okay, Haruka."

msgctxt "724_Haruka"
msgid "When Hamazaki-san was on his deathbed... he asked me to tell\\r\n"
"you something."
msgstr "When Hamazaki-san was on his deathbed... he asked me to tell\\r\n"
"you something."

msgctxt "736_Haruka"
msgid "\"Keep the Tojo Clan safe from the cops. It's the only proof left that guys like us ever existed.\""
msgstr "\"Keep the Tojo Clan safe from the cops. It's the only proof left that guys like us ever existed.\""

msgctxt "748_Kiryu"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "760_Haruka"
msgid "He wanted you to tell Saejima-san, too. That was his dying\\r\n"
"wish."
msgstr "He wanted you to tell Saejima-san, too. That was his dying\\r\n"
"wish."

msgctxt "772_Kiryu"
msgid "Got it. Thanks for telling me all this, Haruka."
msgstr "Got it. Thanks for telling me all this, Haruka."

msgctxt "784_Haruka"
msgid "Of course."
msgstr "No se preocupe."

msgctxt "796_Kiryu"
msgid "By the way. What happened to Hamazaki's body?"
msgstr "By the way. What happened to Hamazaki's body?"

msgctxt "808_Haruka"
msgid "I had them send it back to Morning Glory. Is that okay?"
msgstr "I had them send it back to Morning Glory. Is that okay?"

msgctxt "820_Kiryu"
msgid "Yeah, that's perfect. Sorry you had to go through all this."
msgstr "Yeah, that's perfect. Sorry you had to go through all this."

msgctxt "832_Haruka"
msgid "It's okay. I'll be fine."
msgstr "It's okay. I'll be fine."

msgctxt "844_Kiryu"
msgid "I should be back in Okinawa soon. And once I am, we'll make\\r\n"
"sure he gets a proper burial."
msgstr "I should be back in Okinawa soon. And once I am, we'll make\\r\n"
"sure he gets a proper burial."

msgctxt "856_Haruka"
msgid "Okay."
msgstr "Está bien."

msgctxt "868_Kiryu"
msgid "Talk to you soon."
msgstr "Entonces hablamos en un rato."

msgctxt "940_Date"
msgid "Where's Akiyama?"
msgstr "Where's Akiyama?"

msgctxt "952_Tanimura"
msgid "Over at his office. Said he needed some time alone."
msgstr "Over at his office. Said he needed some time alone."

msgctxt "964_Tanimura"
msgid "Can't say I blame him. Not with how he felt about Yasuko-san."
msgstr "Can't say I blame him. Not with how he felt about Yasuko-san."

msgctxt "976_Date"
msgid "Yeah... I can't imagine."
msgstr "Yeah... I can't imagine."

msgctxt "1000_Date"
msgid "Anyway, what now? Munakata has probably had his paws on that\\r\n"
"file for a while at this point."
msgstr "Anyway, what now? Munakata has probably had his paws on that\\r\n"
"file for a while at this point."

msgctxt "1012_Kiryu"
msgid "Good question."
msgstr "Por qué será."

msgctxt "1048_Tanimura"
msgid "Well, we can't let things end like this, that's for sure."
msgstr "Bueno, no podemos dejar que termine así, eso seguro."

msgctxt "1060_Tanimura"
msgid "Yasuko-san's dead. Munakata's still on the force. And\\r\n"
"nobody's doing a damn thing about it! You think I'm just\\r\n"
"gonna sit around and let that stand!?"
msgstr "Yasuko-san's dead. Munakata's still on the force. And\\r\n"
"nobody's doing a damn thing about it! You think I'm just\\r\n"
"gonna sit around and let that stand!?"

msgctxt "1072_Date"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "1084_Kiryu"
msgid "Tanimura..."
msgstr "Tanimura..."

msgctxt "1144_Kiryu"
msgid "Where are you going?"
msgstr "¿A dónde vas?"

msgctxt "1156_Saejima"
msgid "Don't gotta tell you that."
msgstr "Don't gotta tell you that."

msgctxt "1168_Kiryu"
msgid "Saejima. We have proof now that you didn't commit those\\r\n"
"murders twenty-five years ago. You'll be a free man once we get them to review your case."
msgstr "Saejima. We have proof now that you didn't commit those\\r\n"
"murders twenty-five years ago. You'll be a free man once we get them to review your case."

msgctxt "1180_Saejima"
msgid "Don't give a rat's ass one way or the other. Do whatever ya\\r\n"
"wanna do."
msgstr "Don't give a rat's ass one way or the other. Do whatever ya\\r\n"
"wanna do."

msgctxt "1192_Saejima"
msgid "...I ain't goin' nowhere. Just gonna go get some fresh air."
msgstr "...I ain't goin' nowhere. Just gonna go get some fresh air."

